festival.introText:
Towneley Park Tribute Festival comes to Towneley Park, Burnley, Lancashire!

LIVE MUSIC - FOOD COURT - COCKTAIL & GIN BARS - PHOTO OPS - VIP EXPERIENCE - + MORE

Under 18's must be accompanied by an adult.

reviews.title: Review of Towneley Park Tribute Festival
reviews.body:
friendly polite staff ,well organised, great location, fab music drinks overpriced annoyed that a full bottle of expensive perfume was confiscated because it was in a glass bottle , yet another member of our party didn't get theirs confiscated which was in a glass bottle.
why cant things be put to one side so you can collect later ? 
This was the downside to what otherwise was a great event.!

faqs.question: What happens If I bought a ticket and cannot attend?
faqs.answer:
Unfortunately we can’t issue you with a refund if you can’t make the event due to work commitments or your mates have dropped out. In these circumstances, we advise passing on your tickets privately to avoid losing out on the money spent.

 

Refunds can only be offered if the event is cancelled or postponed, as agreed upon purchase.

faqs.question: When is Towneley Park Tribute Festival 2023?
faqs.answer: Towneley Park Tribute Festival takes place on Sunday 20th August 2023.

faqs.question: What does a VIP ticket include?
faqs.answer: A VIP ticket includes access to VIP area, VIP toilets & bar, and queue jump

faqs.question: Where is Towneley Park Tribute Festival?
faqs.answer: Towneley Park Tribute Festival is located at Towneley Park Burnley BB11 in Burnley.

faqs.question: Does Towneley Park Tribute Festival have any age restrictions?
faqs.answer: No, there are no age restrictions for Towneley Park Tribute Festival, but under 18s must be accompanied by an adult.
